170
00:18:34,230 --> 00:18:36,050
I did?

171
00:18:36,050 --> 00:18:38,630
What do you think about this one? Does the color stand out too much?

172
00:18:38,630 --> 00:18:42,200
It's pretty. It'll be easy to see because it's bright. I was looking at this one.

173
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:44,950
Really? We were on the same page.

174
00:18:46,430 --> 00:18:48,280
You still have that?

175
00:18:48,280 --> 00:18:50,510
I'll tell you something funny.

176
00:18:51,690 --> 00:18:53,780
When I bought this,

177
00:18:54,370 --> 00:18:56,650
I actually didn't really like this color.

178
00:18:56,650 --> 00:19:01,360
