179
00:19:01,360 --> 00:19:03,540
I thought, I should also buy this.

180
00:19:03,540 --> 00:19:09,800
I think I thought that? In any case, I usually don't like bright colors like this.

181
00:19:11,950 --> 00:19:13,660
It's funny, right?

182
00:19:15,120 --> 00:19:19,880
Sometimes I write my diary in here... No, not a diary.

183
00:19:19,880 --> 00:19:24,420
Sometimes I just write memos in it.

184
00:19:27,750 --> 00:19:29,380
Jin Hyeok.

185
00:19:33,590 --> 00:19:35,960
It's a bit embarrassing,

186
00:19:38,990 --> 00:19:41,240
