201
00:20:55,610 --> 00:21:00,090
Jin Hyeok. You're a great person.

202
00:21:00,090 --> 00:21:02,900
You're as great of a person as the CEO is.

203
00:21:02,900 --> 00:21:07,170
So I'm supporting your feelings.

204
00:21:22,710 --> 00:21:24,440
Hye In.

205
00:21:26,130 --> 00:21:28,710
Thank you for liking me.

206
00:21:30,560 --> 00:21:33,640
It's better than saying that you're sorry that you didn't know how I felt.

207
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:35,800
It's less embarrassing.

208
00:21:37,430 --> 00:21:40,310
It was not the time for me to say that.

209
00:21:40,310 --> 00:21:42,550
I told you, don't apologize.

210
00:21:42,550 --> 00:21:45,420
I made a huge decision to tell you this

211
00:21:46,500 --> 00:21:49,980
