216
00:22:09,560 --> 00:22:12,270
Did you commit a sin? Why would you call it turning yourself in?

217
00:22:12,270 --> 00:22:14,700
I know, right? Should I call it coming clean?

218
00:22:14,700 --> 00:22:16,960
That's the same thing.

219
00:22:18,790 --> 00:22:20,640
It's refreshing.

220
00:22:24,320 --> 00:22:26,440
I had a feeling.

221
00:22:27,060 --> 00:22:31,730
