229
00:22:57,260 --> 00:23:01,740
Goodness. This is real gold, 14k.

230
00:23:04,970 --> 00:23:08,080
- Do you not like the design?
- It's my style.

231
00:23:08,080 --> 00:23:10,740
Look at that, I paid careful attention.

232
00:23:10,740 --> 00:23:13,590
