235
00:23:22,080 --> 00:23:29,390
Lee Dae Chan, you know that everyone has different viewpoints. Right?

236
00:23:29,390 --> 00:23:33,010
Not everyone can be the same.

237
00:23:33,010 --> 00:23:35,820
Of course. Everyone is different.

238
00:23:35,820 --> 00:23:39,190
I'm sorry that I end up saying

239
00:23:39,190 --> 00:23:41,650
