242
00:23:51,570 --> 00:23:56,720
Some people transcend those things and dive into another world and experience true love and all that.

243
00:23:56,720 --> 00:23:59,700
But I'm not that kind of person. I'm very realistic.

244
00:23:59,700 --> 00:24:03,160
