276
00:26:13,620 --> 00:26:18,820
At first, I was confused and heart-broken, but

277
00:26:18,820 --> 00:26:22,320
I thought, "I can understand how Mom can feel this way."

278
00:26:22,320 --> 00:26:24,920
You must resent me.

279
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:28,140
No, you can do something like that.

280
00:26:34,520 --> 00:26:37,400
Because you might not know

281
00:26:37,400 --> 00:26:41,060
