288
00:27:15,850 --> 00:27:20,090
She said that our simple home

289
00:27:20,890 --> 00:27:24,630
was priceless, that beautiful masterpiece.

290
00:27:24,630 --> 00:27:28,260
She said she was afraid that it might be destroyed because of her.

291
00:27:28,260 --> 00:27:30,770
So she said to break up.

292
00:27:31,650 --> 00:27:33,810
I ...

293
00:27:35,080 --> 00:27:38,180
I am sorry. What could I do ...

294
00:27:38,180 --> 00:27:43,690
Your feeling is love and her feeling is love, too.

295
00:27:43,690 --> 00:27:46,260
So, Mom ...

296
00:27:46,260 --> 00:27:51,290
I will somehow protect both loves.

297
00:27:51,290 --> 00:27:57,790
Until you understand, until she is free from feeling guilty...

298
00:27:59,340 --> 00:28:03,680
I'm going to wait. In my place.

299
00:28:08,510 --> 00:28:10,680
I guess I was ...

