409
00:39:38,990 --> 00:39:42,140
Don't concern yourself over this.

410
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:56,700
Because it seemed like our homemade food suited your taste.

411
00:39:58,240 --> 00:40:01,730
You must have a lot of worries because of your father's case.

412
00:40:01,730 --> 00:40:06,120
I wish that you would at least eat well.

