424
00:43:15,690 --> 00:43:17,960
However,

425
00:43:19,120 --> 00:43:22,640
those eyes always bothered me.

426
00:43:22,680 --> 00:43:30,530
How should I put it? In Cha Soo Hyeon's eyes, Taegyeong's strength, worth, dignity...

427
00:43:31,960 --> 00:43:35,140
I saw no envy of any of these things.

428
00:43:37,040 --> 00:43:40,160
That always concerned me.

429
00:43:40,210 --> 00:43:42,270
I hated her.

430
00:43:44,060 --> 00:43:46,090
For you ...

