00:43:46,940 --> 00:43:50,330
that is why you hated her.

432
00:43:50,330 --> 00:43:52,390
As for me,

433
00:43:53,570 --> 00:43:56,160
that's why I felt sorry towards Soo Hyeon.

434
00:43:56,160 --> 00:44:01,680
