474
00:48:02,340 --> 00:48:08,020
Somehow I feel you had a more difficult time than I did.

475
00:48:08,020 --> 00:48:10,560
It was very upsetting.

476
00:48:10,560 --> 00:48:14,920
You did come along because this was the road that I've chosen.

